1.body: OpenJDK is the reference implementation of Java SE. Oracle Java SSE Oracle Yes Red Hat build of OpenJDK Red Hat Yes GraalVM Community Edition GraalVM Yes TCK (Technology Compatibility Kit) is a suite of tests that checks for JSR compliance.
